Stellenbosch University student Theuns du Toit will be appealing his expulsion from the institution. eNCA's Monique Mortlock has more details. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Stellenbosch University student Theuns du Toit will be appealing his expulsion from the institution. READ: Du Toit expelled from Stellenbosch University Du Toit has been expelled with immediate effect following a hearing by the university’s independent Central Disciplinary Committee. He was caught on camera urinating on fellow student Babalo Ndwayana’s belongings in May. Watch the video above for more details on this story.